data.description: Beautiful brick townhome overlooking scenic woods and wetlands.  Spacious and open floor plan with 9-foot ceilings. Cozy great room featuring a gas fireplace that opens into the kitchen and dining area. The amazing kitchen boasts an abundance of cabinets for storage and is accented by stainless steel appliances.  Laminate wood flooring and tile floors throughout. Two upstairs bedrooms are divided by a generous sized loft perfect for a TV room or home office. Primary bedroom has walk-in closet and a serene, wooded view. Maintenance-free living at its best. New roof was installed. Located close to all that Williamsburg has to offer.
